ibliothèque du Congrès</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://d-nb.info/gnd/118576089">Gemeinsame Normdatei</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://id.ndl.go.jp/auth/ndlna/00448491">Bibliothèque nationale de la Diète</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://catalogo.bne.es/uhtbin/authoritybrowse.cgi?action=display&amp;authority_id=XX910282">Bibliothèque nationale d’Espagne</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://data.bibliotheken.nl/id/thes/p069003610">Bibliothèque royale des Pays-Bas</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://uli.nli.org.il/F/?func=direct&amp;doc_number=000087471&amp;local_base=nlx10">Bibliothèque nationale d’Israël</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://nukat.edu.pl/aut/n%20%2093126851">Bibliothèque universitaire de Pologne</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://cantic.bnc.cat/registres/CUCId/a10394552">Bibliothèque nationale de Catalogne</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://libris.kb.se/auth/225586">Bibliothèque nationale de Suède</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://viaf.org/processed/BAV%7CADV10120103">Bibliothèque apostolique vaticane</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://nla.gov.au/anbd.aut-an35321598">Bibliothèque nationale d’Australie</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://authority.bibsys.no/authority/rest/authorities/html/90075325">Base de bibliothèque norvégienne</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://katalog.nsk.hr/F/?func=direct&amp;doc_number=000013967&amp;local_base=nsk10">Bibliothèque universitaire de Zagreb</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n79-018814">WorldCat</a></span></li></ul></div></li>
